  <section>
    <h2>FAQs</h2>
    <h3>How much does it cost to build a delivery web portal?</h3>
    <p>It depends on complexity. A simple portal can cost a few thousand dollars, while advanced solutions with GPS and automation may cost more.</p>

    <h3>Do I need coding knowledge to build it?</h3>
    <p>No. You can use ready-made CMS platforms like WordPress with WooCommerce or hire developers for custom solutions.</p>

    <h3>Which payment gateways should I integrate?</h3>
    <p>Popular options include Stripe, PayPal, and local banking integrations depending on your target region.</p>
